    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a solid choice for someone needing a reliable car for daily commuting. While it runs well and has been regularly serviced, the exterior shows its age with some clear coat peeling on the hood and a few minor dents. The interior is clean but shows noticeable wear on the driver's seat and carpet. It\u2019s a dependable workhorse that\u2019s ready for many more miles, provided you don't mind a bit of character in its appearance.",
